		<guid isPermaLink="false">http://www.adsalestips.com/?p=2405</guid>
		<description><![CDATA[If you can sell then you will never be out or work, why not try a career in advertising sales, the advertising industry is crying out [&#8230;]]]></description>
				<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>If you can sell then you will never be out or work, why not try a career in advertising sales, the advertising industry is crying out for new and fresh talent, as a young person looking to start a career and fast track into creating your own wealth and control you future, advertising sales is the perfect career.</p>
<p>Four points you need to learn to become a great sales person</p>
<p>1. Making appointments: Getting the right appointments is 50% of the way to closing the deal<br />
2. The Sales process: Introduction, questioning, listening, presenting &amp; closing<br />
3. Handling objections: Learn to be able to manage objection to your advantage<br />
4. Closing techniques: Learn how and when to close the deal</p>
<p>adsalestips.com is the most coherent online advertising sales platform that will provide you the tools, skills and foundations to starting a career in advertising sales, all videos come with my personal notes</p>
<p>Start your career today!</p>
]]></content:encoded>
